    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="proctype" graphiccount="0">
        <title>GLOW PLUG ASSISTED START</title>
        <para>This feature increases engine startability in cold weather. The glow plugs are controlled by the
            Electronic Control Module which monitors engine temperature. "A WAIT TO START" lamp is included to inform
            the operator when the engine is ready for cranking.
        </para>
